Title: Kazima Attar Honeysuckle Non Alcoholic Eau de Parfum  -  10 ml(For Men, Women)
Description: Honeysuckle are arching shrubs or twining vines in the family Caprifoliaceae, native to the Northern Hemisphere. There are about 180 species of honeysuckle, with by far the greatest diversity in China, where over 100 species occur; by comparison, Europe and North America have only about 20 native species each. Widely known species include Lonicera periclymenum (European Honeysuckle or Woodbine), Lonicera japonica (Japanese Honeysuckle, White Honeysuckle, or Chinese Honeysuckle) and Lonicera sempervirens (Coral Honeysuckle, Trumpet Honeysuckle, or Woodbine Honeysuckle). Hummingbirds are attracted to these plants.

Encased in a stylish, sleek flacon, F from Salvatore Ferragamo is a scent that makes your romantic evening more special. F is certainly what success smells like, what real men smell like.

Created by perfumers Sonia Constant, Nathalie Gracia-Cetto and Antoine Maisondieu in February 2010, Burberry Sport is the epitome of liveliness. The vibrant and sporty fragrance is contained in a colored glass flacon with a rubber trim in keeping with the theme of the Burberry sports line. Title: Hugo Boss EDT - 100 ml(For Men)
Description: Fresh, urbane and entirely masculine, he is a man who believes in himself. He knows what he is capable of and pushes his boundaries to find out what he can achieve. Hugo Boss adorns him with Hugo, a luxury fragrance that is a class apart, just like him. The delicacy of the Eau de Toilette portrays the diligence that he exerts; from the family of aromatic greens, this fragrance is one that colors memories of a long summer day. Hugo was created in 1995 under the able guidance of famed perfumer, Bob Aliano. Reminiscent of a clean, scented breeze that blows in from a tiny yet beautiful kitchen garden, the opening notes of lavender, green apple, mint, grapefruit and basil leave you yearning for yet another sunlit morning spent by the patio. As the heart notes of carnation, sage, geranium and jasmine trail into a strong yet subtle dry down of patchouli, fir and cedar, the intensity of the fragrance gets you with its radiant aura. A tinge of sharpness that it departs with uplifts your mood even at the end of a busy working day leaving you fresh and ready for the adventures that seek you out. The transparent glass vial seems to reflect the extracts of the choicest ingredients that go into the creation of this masterpiece. Trust in your own individuality; indulge your senses in the challenging redolence of Hugo.

Description: Dolce & Gabbana introduces L'Eau The One a covetable, uplifting new fragrance that carries on the lavish legacy of the original The One, and adds a fruity, head-turning twist. This modern, warm, oriental-floral essence embodies the glamorous diva, but with a lighter mood. She is undeniably seductive and eye-catching with a refreshing attitude of winsome ease. The sleek, contemporary bottle, with its refined white gold finish, reflects the sophisticated charm of the woman who is, and will always be the one.

Title: Versace Eros EDT  -  100 ml(For Men)

The aim of this edition is to reveal and release unrestrained passion and to accentuate desire. The fragrance was named after Greek god of love and son of goddess Aphrodite - Eros. Inspiration by ancient Greece has lasted since the time when Gianni Versace raised his fashion empire and took goddess Medusa as symbol of the brand to adorn numerous products of the house, among them also the new flacon of mens fragrance Eros.

Title: HERRERA by Carolina Herrera EDT SPRAY 6.7 OZ for MEN

She likes her cars fast and her perfumes luxurious which is why she favors Carolina Herrera 212 VIP, the bottled essence of her. Created by master perfumer Alberto Morillas, the Eau de Parfum rounds off her volatile personality and earns her well-deserved glances of envy. She is young, wild and free and always ready to party. The volatile cocktail of the opening notes have a suffused, wild quality induced by the accords of passionfruit and rum which deepen into dark, musky heart notes accentuated by gardenia. The base note firmly hooks onto your senses with tonka bean and creamy, alluring vanilla. She is the star; she knows it, she enjoys it and she is addicted to it. The dazzling, gold sheen on the unique bottle only adds to her desirability and the magnetic cap seems to reflect how you are drawn to her. Overwhelming and intoxicating, she will steal all the attention and you won’t even mind.

Description: By day, he is the perfect gentleman; he does his duty, files his reports and is always on time. But by night, he is the ultimate symbol of masculinity; virile and powerful, lounging on the couches of his favorite haunts and prowling around for his next prey. When his magnetic eyes alight on something that catches his fancy, neither hell nor high water can stop him from reaching out and taking it. Azzaro presents Silver Black for the tall, dark and handsome stranger who knows all the tricks in the book. His soft charm combines with the intoxicating tones of his luxury fragrance to render you helpless in its fiery wake. The Eau de Toilette was created by famed perfumer Francoise Caron and launched in 2005. Wanton lust takes precedence in the opening notes of lime, apple, anise and bergamot. A fearful episode of your past that you would hate to repeat. You can try to overcome those stress-addled moments and panic attacks with the help of this refreshing fragrance. Description: Fresh and tropical, Jennifer Lopez Blue Glow radiates a buoyant charm onto the vibrant woman who dons this luxury scent. A whiff of Blue Glow transports you to an isolated beach with nothing but the calming sound of the sea and smooth sea shells grazing your path. This Eau de Toilette is created under the joint collaboration of Jennifer Lopez and Coty Prestige. It opens with a top note of sweet and tangy mangosteen, citrusy orange and fruity hints of cranberry blossom. Following into a delicate heart note of light fragrant water lily, sweetly intense tincture of rose and floral notes of orchid. Ultimately, the base note brings together a composition of strong scents that weave together earthy oakmoss, fragrant sandalwood, antique touches of mahogany, aromatic virginia cedar and tonka bean that bursts with subtle hints of almond, vanilla and coumarin. This fragrance that simmers with diverse natural ingredients brings forth an interesting aroma with woody, floral and watery accords. The elegantly curved shape of the bottle is painted a deep oceanic blue and tastefully decorated with fine jewellery. The perfume swirling in the blue tinted bottle gives you a feel of gentle waves touching the shoreline. The carefree woman dabs on Jennifer Lopez Blue Glow to add just a little more sparkle to her relaxing mornings.
